          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the Minister for giving way. He said something very important, which perhaps he could briefly explain. He described a Cabinet decision of 50 per cent. It would be enormously helpful to the Committee if the Minister could explain to what the 50 per cent refers.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-07290'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040331_GCR_53'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040331_GCR_53' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew McIntosh' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
