            The Minister did not address the issue I raised in regard to the <a href="/acts/trustee-savings-banks-act-1985">Trustee Savings Banks Act 1985</a> and why merely ordering a reconstruction of the TSB is not wholly appropriate in this context, particularly given the unanimity about the direction in which we wish to see the Tote move. There was no need for us to nationalise the TSB, with a promise to subsequently privatise it, but there was an opportunity significantly
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_468gc' title='Col. 468GC &mdash; HL Deb 31 March 2004 vol 659 c468GC' name='column_468gc' href='#column_468gc' rel='bookmark'>468GC</a>
