            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_478gc' title='Col. 478GC &mdash; HL Deb 31 March 2004 vol 659 c478GC' name='column_478gc' href='#column_478gc' rel='bookmark'>478GC</a>
            Trust's ownership, so we cannot guarantee a figure, but our intention is that it should continue on broadly the same basis.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
